		8.10.8 Water

Relevant Items:
Robe of the Sea (req Con4, W3, Chest slot)
Water Bracelet (req Con6, W1, Misc. slot)

Relevant Summons:
Bind Ice Devil (req B3W3) W3 (1 in 6 chance of S2)
